rows.label: tlk45300157_03_msg0001
rows.name:
The surface temperature of
Superbia has been slowly
but surely rising lately.

rows.label: tlk45300157_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Shamayim Plant has been around
ever since the capital was first
moved here to Hadashal...

rows.label: tlk45300157_03_msg0003
rows.name:
In the past century, we've
recorded an overall temperature
increase of 6 points.

rows.label: tlk45300157_03_msg0004
rows.name:
In Gula for comparison, we only have
data for the last decade, but the
temperature rose by just 0.01 points.

rows.label: tlk45300157_03_msg0005
rows.name:
So you can see why the
Empire might be in a hurry
to expand their territory.
